---
export const prerender = true;
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
    <meta name="robots" content="noindex,nofollow" />
    <meta name="theme-color" content="#222321" />
    <title>Gold Concentrator 内容后台</title>
    <style>
      html,
      body {
        min-height: 100%;
        margin: 0;
        background: #f4f0e8;
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      }

      .cms-help,
      noscript {
        max-width: 680px;
        margin: 80px auto;
        padding: 24px;
        color: #fffdf8;
        background: #222321;
      }

      .cms-help h1 {
        margin-top: 0;
        color: #efc56d;
      }

      .cms-help a {
        color: #efc56d;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="cms-help" id="cms-help">
      <h1>Gold Concentrator 内容后台</h1>
      <p>后台正在加载。首次使用时，请通过已授权的 GitHub 账户登录。</p>
      <p>
        上传图片、文章、案例和视频前，可先阅读
        <a
          href="https://github.com/fironwoo/goldconcentrator.com/blob/main/docs/cms-publishing-guide-zh.md"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
        >
          中文操作指南
        </a>。
      </p>
    </div>
    <noscript>内容后台需要启用 JavaScript。请启用后重新打开本页。</noscript>
    <script is:inline src="https://unpkg.com/@sveltia/cms/dist/sveltia-cms.js"></script>
    <script>
      import '../../scripts/admin-help';
    </script>
  </body>
</html>
